# removed inadvertently-committed local session artifacts (PII containment).
# These ignore the artifact CLASSES, not just the current filenames — the repo-wide
# `!docs/**` unignore above would otherwise let a regenerated transcript/plan (a new
# date, a new run) become trackable again. Glob the classes so containment is durable.
docs/planning/session-exports/
docs/brainstorm/brainstorm--transcript--*.md
docs/planning/premortem-transcript-*.md
docs/planning/planning--*prompts*.md
docs/planning/planning--ai-session-audit--*.md
.codex/plans/**/*-prompts.md
.codex/plans/*-gtm-role-prompts.md
.claude/plans/**/*ai-session-audit*.md
